title: Get Ready for ChatGPT-Style AI Chatbots That Do Your Boring Chores
description: Move over, Siri. Startups are using the technology behind ChatGPT to build more capable AI agents that can control your computer and access the web to get things done—with sometimes chaotic results.

title: The Fall of Babylon Is a Warning for AI Unicorns
description: When it went public in 2021, Babylon Health was valued at over $4 billion. Now it has declared bankruptcy. Insiders say it could never live up to its hype.

title: TikTok Shop Has a Snail Slime Problem
description: TikTok Shop, which launched in the US last week, is littered with impossibly cheap—and fake—products. Snail slime is just the beginning.

title: Universal Music Declares War on Streaming Noise
description: The world’s largest record label has struck a deal in France to demonetize “functional music” like AI sludge and noise tracks and give more money to artists.
